reviewText: This says it all !!  I have been to Medjugorje, Croatia and have had miracles happen.  Part of my rosaries went from silver to gold as soon as I knelt down in St. James church !!!!!!!!!!!!

This is what I was looking for.  I wanted a video that talked about the apparition and told what the children saw and what Mary's message was.  I'm planning on showing it at our church.  Great for all ages!
